=================
Dagster Webserver
=================

Usage
~~~~~

Eg in dagster_examples

.. code-block:: sh

  dagster-webserver -p 3333

Running dev ui:

.. code-block:: sh

  NEXT_PUBLIC_BACKEND_ORIGIN="http://localhost:3333" yarn start
